  {
   "start": 442.98,
   "end": 449.04,
   "text": "I can sit on my table here and work."
  },
  {
   "start": 451.16,
   "end": 452.36,
   "text": "However..."
  },
  {
   "start": 452.36,
   "end": 462.84,
   "text": "I'm hell-bent intent on making the computer work secondary to the bicycling."
  },
  {
   "start": 464.44,
   "end": 467.84,
   "text": "Because biking here, where I am, is..."
  },
  {
   "start": 467.84,
   "end": 469.16,
   "text": "I'll say where I am."
  },
  {
   "start": 469.24,
   "end": 470.02,
   "text": "I'm outside of my web."
  },
  {
   "start": 470.74,
   "end": 471.62,
   "text": "Fucking awesome."
  },
  {
   "start": 474.42,
   "end": 475.2,
   "text": "Trails everywhere."
  },
  {
   "start": 475.2,
   "end": 475.76,
   "text": "Or..."
  },
  {
   "start": 475.76,
   "end": 476.86,
   "text": "I was biking today."
  },
  {
   "start": 476.94,
   "end": 477.94,
   "text": "I did the course today."
  },
  {
   "start": 479.44,
   "end": 480.28,
   "text": "Just..."
  },
  {
   "start": 480.28,
   "end": 481.04,
   "text": "My God."
  },
  {
   "start": 481.76,
   "end": 482.64,
   "text": "Banked turns."
  },
  {
   "start": 484.64,
   "end": 486.06,
   "text": "Going so fast."
  },
  {
   "start": 487.14,
   "end": 488.28,
   "text": "Zooming through sand pits."
  },
  {
   "start": 488.4,
   "end": 489.52,
   "text": "Going up..."
  },
  {
   "start": 489.52,
   "end": 490.52,
   "text": "Uh..."
  },
  {
   "start": 490.52,
   "end": 491.38,
   "text": "Fucking..."
  },
  {
   "start": 491.38,
   "end": 492.94,
   "text": "Terraced..."
  },
  {
   "start": 492.94,
   "end": 493.9,
   "text": "Sandstone."
  },
  {
   "start": 494.98,
   "end": 495.42,
   "text": "Uh..."
  },
  {
   "start": 495.42,
   "end": 496.02,
   "text": "Steep-ass..."
  },
  {
   "start": 496.02,
   "end": 496.88,
   "text": "You know, I mean..."
  },
  {
   "start": 496.88,
   "end": 497.32,
   "text": "Woof!"
  },
  {
   "start": 497.8,
   "end": 498.56,
   "text": "Workout, baby."
  },
  {
   "start": 499.72,
   "end": 500.44,
   "text": "Um..."
  },
  {
   "start": 500.44,
   "end": 501.28,
   "text": "And it's just..."
  },
  {
   "start": 501.28,
   "end": 501.8,
   "text": "Adventure."
  },
  {
   "start": 502.04,
   "end": 502.3,
   "text": "I..."
  },
  {
   "start": 502.3,
   "end": 502.98,
   "text": "I mean..."
  },
  {
   "start": 502.98,
   "end": 504.98,
   "text": "I could be here forever and not let it..."
  },
  {
   "start": 504.98,
   "end": 505.52,
   "text": "No, the trails."
  },
  {
   "start": 506.52,
   "end": 507.18,
   "text": "Did you hear that?"
  },
  {
   "start": 507.3,
   "end": 507.56,
   "text": "Thunder."
  },
  {
   "start": 508.32,
   "end": 509.58,
   "text": "And then you hit the trail."
  },
  {
   "start": 511.28,
   "end": 512.14,
   "text": "It's starting to rain again."
  },
  {
   "start": 512.54,
   "end": 513.64,
   "text": "And then you hit the trail."
  },
  {
   "start": 514.54,
   "end": 515.48,
   "text": "And then you learn the trail."
  },
  {
   "start": 515.54,
   "end": 516.48,
   "text": "And then you want to do the trail again."
  },
  {
   "start": 516.54,
   "end": 517.3,
   "text": "Because now you know the trail."
  },
  {
   "start": 517.36,
   "end": 518.32,
   "text": "And then you want to do the trail faster."
  },
  {
   "start": 519.72,
   "end": 520.16,
   "text": "So..."
  },
  {
   "start": 520.16,
   "end": 525.7,
   "text": "And then I go home and I'm only going to do the internet work as just something to keep"
  },
  {
   "start": 525.7,
   "end": 526.22,
   "text": "Me occupied."
  },
  {
   "start": 527.62,
   "end": 528.14,
   "text": "Um..."
  },
  {
   "start": 528.14,
   "end": 528.84,
   "text": "Because I..."
  },
  {
   "start": 528.84,
   "end": 534.74,
   "text": "I consider myself way ahead of schedule as far as development of my website is concerned."
  },
  {
   "start": 535.74,
   "end": 536.34,
   "text": "Um..."
  },
  {
   "start": 536.34,
   "end": 542.3,
   "text": "I've got so many projects that are, like, well into the project."
  },
  {
   "start": 543.1,
   "end": 545.1,
   "text": "I've got it saved on my mom's external."
  },
  {
   "start": 547.18,
   "end": 548.78,
   "text": "My external is here with me."
  },
  {
   "start": 550.87,
   "end": 555.13,
   "text": "I think I'm going to burn a bunch of CDs whenever I get around to it."
  },
  {
   "start": 555.67,
   "end": 557.39,
   "text": "And, like, mail them back to my mom."
  },
  {
   "start": 558.81,
   "end": 559.71,
   "text": "Just so that I don't..."
  },
  {
   "start": 559.71,
   "end": 561.71,
   "text": "Oh, well, it's also backed up on the web..."
  },
  {
   "start": 561.71,
   "end": 563.63,
   "text": "On the server as well, so..."
  },
  {
   "start": 563.63,
   "end": 567.18,
   "text": "But anyways, um..."
  },
  {
   "start": 567.18,
   "end": 568.16,
   "text": "No, it's raining here, though."
  },
  {
   "start": 568.8,
   "end": 570.92,
   "text": "I was just, like, sitting here in my car."
  },
  {
   "start": 571.54,
   "end": 576.34,
   "text": "Just, like, watching these, like, rivers of water come down on that side."
  },
  {
   "start": 577.24,
   "end": 579.42,
   "text": "Like, there's a sand pit right here."
  },
  {
   "start": 579.48,
   "end": 580.66,
   "text": "I'm in the middle of a sand pit."
  },
  {
   "start": 580.92,
   "end": 583.26,
   "text": "In a little, like, juniper forest."
  },
  {
   "start": 584.28,
   "end": 585.84,
   "text": "Like, cliffs over there."
  },
  {
   "start": 586.28,
   "end": 587.66,
   "text": "Fucking amazing, man."
  },
  {
   "start": 589.2,
   "end": 589.84,
   "text": "Um..."
  },
  {
   "start": 589.84,
   "end": 591.0,
   "text": "Just looking out of the window."
  },
  {
   "start": 591.32,
   "end": 592.5,
   "text": "Just watching it rain around me."
  },
  {
   "start": 592.54,
   "end": 593.3,
   "text": "Just being like..."
  },
  {
   "start": 593.3,
   "end": 593.66,
   "text": "Ho-ho!"
  },
  {
   "start": 593.66,
   "end": 595.6,
   "text": "You know?"
  },
  {
   "start": 595.8,
   "end": 598.86,
   "text": "And, like, maybe 15 years ago or whatever, I would have been like..."
  },
  {
   "start": 598.86,
   "end": 600.44,
   "text": "Eh, gotten bored after a day or two."
  },
  {
   "start": 601.18,
   "end": 602.32,
   "text": "Fuck no, not now, dude."
  },
  {
   "start": 602.34,
   "end": 603.14,
   "text": "I've got the computer."
  },
  {
   "start": 603.68,
   "end": 605.08,
   "text": "I've got the electrical outlet."
  },
  {
   "start": 606.4,
   "end": 607.56,
   "text": "I mean..."
  },
  {
   "start": 607.56,
   "end": 608.32,
   "text": "Bang!"
  },
  {
   "start": 608.42,
   "end": 610.08,
   "text": "There's nothing to distract me."
  },
  {
   "start": 610.44,
   "end": 611.94,
   "text": "I don't have internet connection here."
  },
  {
   "start": 612.36,
   "end": 613.84,
   "text": "I don't have cell phone connection."
  },
  {
   "start": 614.46,
   "end": 616.16,
   "text": "I haven't seen a single person here."
  },
  {
   "start": 617.36,
   "end": 618.56,
   "text": "I mean..."
  },
  {
   "start": 618.56,
   "end": 623.17,
   "text": "I'm gonna get some shit done, man."
  },
  {
   "start": 623.17,
   "end": 624.55,
   "text": "And I'm gonna get fit."
  },
  {
   "start": 625.21,
   "end": 629.35,
   "text": "I'm 176 pounds right now, and I want to drop down to 155."
  },
  {
   "start": 630.27,
   "end": 631.27,
   "text": "Because I want to do..."
  },
  {
   "start": 631.27,
   "end": 632.61,
   "text": "I want to be a bike racer next year."
  },
  {
   "start": 632.77,
   "end": 633.31,
   "text": "If I can..."
  },
  {
   "start": 633.31,
   "end": 634.73,
   "text": "Well, I think I can afford it, too."
  },
  {
   "start": 635.31,
   "end": 637.77,
   "text": "Because I got the passive income, and I'm not spending anything."
  },
  {
   "start": 638.95,
   "end": 639.51,
   "text": "So..."
  },
  {
   "start": 639.51,
   "end": 641.47,
   "text": "I'm not gonna do a lot of bike races."
  },
  {
   "start": 642.55,
   "end": 643.31,
   "text": "I'm out of time."
  },
  {
   "start": 643.97,
   "end": 644.93,
   "text": "Anyways, that's my new show."
  },
  {
   "start": 645.01,
   "end": 646.01,
   "text": "Living in the car with Kyle."
  },
  {
   "start": 646.01,
   "end": 675.99,
   "text": "I'm out of time."
  }
 ]
